<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FootValue Scanner</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 min-h-screen p-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-4xl">⚽</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">FootValue Scanner</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl p-6 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">🔥 Meilleures Value Bets (Live)</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium">Liverpool - Arsenal</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Over 2.5 buts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xl">2.15</div>
            <div class="text-emerald-500 text-sm font-bold">+14% Value</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium">PSG - Monaco</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">PSG gagne</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xl">1.68</div>
            <div class="text-emerald-500 text-sm font-bold">+11% Value</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-4">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium">Real Madrid - Betis</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Both Teams To Score</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xl">1.95</div>
            <div class="text-emerald-500 text-sm font-bold">+9% Value</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500 rounded-3xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-orange-400 font-semibold mb-2">🚨 Alerte Chaude</h3>
      <p class="text-lg">Manchester City à 1.58 (probabilité estimée 78%)</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-orange-300">Cote anormalement haute sur un énorme favori</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-12">
      FootValue Scanner • Démo mobile • Rafraîchissement auto
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
